# design refs — Figma exports, mockups (local only; Figma is canonical).
# Ignore the CONTENTS (design/*, not design/) so the negation below can
# re-include a file — git can't re-include through an excluded *directory*.
design/*
# …except committed design DOCS (e.g. the glass-card component spec, which
# SPEC.md V36 + code comments reference — must ship so those refs resolve).
!design/GLASS-CARD.md
